org.apache.flex.abc.semantics

Class PooledValue

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flex.abc.semantics.PooledValue

  • public class PooledValue
extends Object
    A representation of a value in a constant pool that is not a name, namespace, or namespace set.

      • setPoolIndex

        public void setPoolIndex(int index)
        Set the value's pool index. This is done when the object that owns this PooledValue, e.g., a MethodInfo, gets to its visitEnd() event and registers all its constant information with the ABCEmitter's constant pools.
